title: Merry Christmas
author: rydenstrife
pages:
#- Merry Christmas you
uncreative lump of pixels. I ought to leave you something as unexciting as the message you left for what you might want which was "suprise me," if you recall. BUT. I am a nice person and the HOLLY JOLLY SPIRIT OF JESUS TELLS ME THAT  
#- YOU MEANT WELL, ARCANECRAFT2 What happened to ArcaneCraft1? Murderer. Look. I'm gonna throw you a bone here. I know the limit is 20d but I'm gonna make an exception because God talks to me in my sleep.
#- You are being gifted historic items from the PapaPound-era battle that ended in retardom on count of the group not being able to function as one and despite Papa's best cheeto-encrusted intentions, it just didn't happen. While in the bunker, I found this 
#- in an unprotected chest. It is the mixed prot of HCF members. It is with a heavy heart I give these items away, but seeing as I do not play this game anymore (and only signed on to give you a gift), I present this to you. Don't fucking lose it. 
#- Don't fucking break it.
Don't fucking sell it.

luv,

ur thecret thanta

ps. The coords to the prot is 1206 58 8052

pss i just realized your ign is arcanecraft4 not 2 lol
#- psss its ryden.
#- 